    <item>
      <title>拉马福萨将反对派焚烧国旗的选举广告称为叛国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ramaphosa-labels-opposition-flag-burning-election-ad-treasonous</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨指责主要反对党犯有叛国罪，因为该党投放了一幅显示国旗被焚烧的选举广告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ramaphosa-labels-opposition-flag-burning-election-ad-treasonous</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国出货量下降 台湾对美出口创纪录增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/taiwan-exports-to-us-jump-by-record-as-china-shipments-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，台湾对美国的出口创历史新高，而对中国大陆的出口却下降，突显出世界两大经济体之间的技术供应链正在加速脱钩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/taiwan-exports-to-us-jump-by-record-as-china-shipments-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:14:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰真理报称，大亨科洛莫伊斯基被指控下令打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/tycoon-kolomoisky-accused-of-ordering-hit-ukrainska-pravda-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据媒体报道，乌克兰当局怀疑商人伊戈尔·科洛莫伊斯基（Igor Kolomoisky）在二十多年前组织了一次未遂的合同杀人事件，这为这位曾经支持弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）的入狱大亨增添了新的潜在刑事责任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/tycoon-kolomoisky-accused-of-ordering-hit-ukrainska-pravda-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 08:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪指控安巴尼和阿达尼向反对党提供非法现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/modi-alleges-ambani-adani-giving-opposition-party-illegal-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理纳伦德拉·莫迪表示，主要反对党从亿万富翁穆克什·安巴尼和高塔姆·阿达尼那里收受非法现金，以资助其竞选活动，这一令人惊讶的指控发生在一场激烈的投票战中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/modi-alleges-ambani-adani-giving-opposition-party-illegal-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 08:16:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国商业游说团体加入降息呼吁，下调 GDP 预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/thai-business-lobby-joins-rate-cut-call-as-it-trims-gdp-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国最大的商业游说团体在大幅下调自己对经济增长的预期后，敦促央行降息，并与政府合作寻找重振商业和消费活动的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/thai-business-lobby-joins-rate-cut-call-as-it-trims-gdp-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 08:05:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国核监督机构在重要报告发布前警告伊朗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/un-nuclear-watchdog-puts-iran-on-notice-ahead-of-key-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗只有几周的时间来遵守联合国核监督机构发出的监测要求，否则将面临新一轮外交谴责的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/un-nuclear-watchdog-puts-iran-on-notice-ahead-of-key-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 07:14:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港政府赢得禁止流行抗议歌曲的上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/hong-kong-court-approves-government-ban-of-protest-song</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港一家法院允许政府禁止用于犯罪目的的流行抗议歌曲，此举可能会引发人们对言论自由减弱的担忧，并引发香港互联网公司的合规问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/hong-kong-court-approves-government-ban-of-protest-song</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 07:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国在最新一次针对政客的袭击后处于高度戒备状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/german-authorities-on-alert-after-latest-attack-on-politician</link>
      <description><![CDATA[柏林一位州部长兼前市长遭到一名身份不明的袭击者的袭击，德国当局正在展开调查，这是下个月欧洲议会选举前政治暴力事件激增的最新证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/german-authorities-on-alert-after-latest-attack-on-politician</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 05:22:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国因拉法入侵计划暂停向以色列运送武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/us-paused-weapons-shipment-to-israel-over-rafah-invasion-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名高级政府官员表示，由于担心对加沙城市拉法可能发动军事进攻，美国暂停了向以色列运送炸弹，而总统乔·拜登反对此举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/us-paused-weapons-shipment-to-israel-over-rafah-invasion-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:02:03 GMT</pubDate>
